Psionics
Psionic abilities draw on ISP (Inner Strength Points), a psychic energy pool
regenerated through rest and meditation. Unlike PPE (magic), ISP is a personal
resource that cannot be stolen or drained by most supernatural forces.

To use a psionic ability:
  psi <power name> [target]
  psi <power name> <target>

Examples:
  psi telepathy Sal
  psi mind bolt brodkil
  psi bio-regeneration
  psi psi-sword

Available psionic powers (cost in ISP):
  PHYSICAL / COMBAT:
    psi-sword             10 ISP : Blade of psionic energy (3d6 MDC, 2 min)
    mind bolt              6 ISP : Psionic energy bolt (3d6 MDC)
    mind bolt heavy       12 ISP : Heavy psionic bolt (6d6 MDC)
    pyrokinesis            6 ISP : Flame touch (1d6 SDC)
    pyrokinesis bolt      12 ISP : Fire bolt (3d6 MDC, ranged)
    pyrokinesis blast     20 ISP : Fire explosion (6d6 MDC, area)
    telekinesis            2 ISP : Move objects without touching

  SENSITIVE / DETECTION:
    telepathy              4 ISP : Read surface thoughts of a target
    empathy                4 ISP : Sense emotional state of a target
    object read            6 ISP : Read history of an object
    sense evil             2 ISP : Detect evil in the room
    sixth sense            2 ISP : Combat warning: +6 init, +2 parry, +3 dodge
    detect psionics        6 ISP : Detect psionic activity nearby

  HEALING / PROTECTION:
    bio-regeneration      10 ISP : Heal 2d6 MDC or 4d6 SDC/HP (self)
    healing touch          6 ISP : Heal 1d8 SDC or 2 HP (touch, other)
    psychic diagnosis      4 ISP : Diagnose wounds and illness
    increased healing      0 ISP : Passively enhances natural healing rate
    deaden pain            4 ISP : Remove penalties from wounds
    psychic surgery       14 ISP : Restore serious injuries
    induce sleep           4 ISP : Put target to sleep (save negates)
    mind block             4 ISP : Block psionic attacks (10 min)

ISP recovers at 2 per hour normally, or 6 per hour while resting.
Meditation (meditate command) restores ISP faster.

Not all powers are available to every psionic OCC. Your OCC determines
which powers you start with and how many ISP you have.

Type psihelp for a quick psionic help index. Telepathy to another player
requires mutual recognition through introduce.

